      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOUGH CALL (1) stalked the lead from a middle box before hitting the front turning and lifting to score (17.50) at this track in a Maiden over 300m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. WOW GIRL (2) was safely held in tougher company last start after settling off pace at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 4 lengths at this track (17.49) beating Koda Mulwee in a Grade 5 on March 21. Can figure in the finish. BLAZING BISCUIT (5) scored (17.51) last time out at this track adding to an already respectable career. In great recent form and expected to measure up again. KAWASAKI GIRL (8) comes into calculations after placing at this track and distance most recently.",
